Memes, memes everywhere! 🙌🏻 The World’s First Meme Museum by 9GAG brings your favorite memes to the real world!⠀
⠀
💌 You are all invited! The 9GAG x @K11ArtMall Meme experience shows you the evolution of memes through imagery, 3D figures, and even scent. 🎥 Here’s a VIP virtual tour for everyone who can’t make it this time cos we’re never gonna give you up!⠀
⠀
Meme Museum by 9GAG⠀
📍K11 Art Mall chi K11 art space, Hong Kong⠀
🗓Jul 16 - Sep 5, 2021⠀
🎫Free entry. Register now #RSVP 👉🏻 Link In Bio⠀
⠀
📹 @jlouofficial⠀
⠀
#K11ARTMALL #WHYSOMEME #MemeMuseum #9GAG
